    "body": "> See #4205 for a more direct fix of the bug.\n\nI don't understand how that prevents Pandoc from wrapping lines internally during Markdown parsing, am I missing something?  From Pandoc user document `By default, text is wrapped appropriately for the output format.`\n\nNew lines get added anywhere in the Markdown to Latex process (not just headers) where the line length surpasses `--columns=NUMBER`\n"
